{"tid":1132523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瑞典斯坦] 街頭藝術家因指出伊斯蘭移民問題，被判「仇恨思想罪」入獄","createTime":"2019-04-30T11:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T13:57:40.000Z","uid":64191,"like":4,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9a54d1f20214763d7d89c13350876c65a1f5aa49","tid":1132523,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"瑞典街頭藝術家Dan Park 曾經於Twitter指「強姦文化係中東及北非人既基本文化」而被判仇恨罪，入獄三個月。<br />\n<br />\n而呢位藝術家亦因為指伊斯蘭移民係&rdquo;Blatter&rdquo;，響瑞典文意思係「居住北歐、未有融入當地既中東及北非裔移民，都有機會係潛在犯罪集團」，而被判囚。<br />\n<br />\n日前，瑞典上訴庭駁回地方法院判決，將其中兩項無罪判決認定有罪，另呢位藝術家刑期從三個月增至四個月。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典現時會對發佈批評穆斯林言論既國民，以「仇恨罪」為名判監，舊年一名70歲婦人因在facebook發表擔心伊斯蘭人會接管國家既言論，而被警察審問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.infowars.com/swedish-artists-jail-term-extended-after-he-committed-hate-crime-of-saying-muslim-migrants-have-not-integrated/?fbclid=IwAR23KWuvsqaYAq3n4n8dAIGDrgmlUwMbjWBVQPSoNbWvUOokuQxD-nxkZz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infowars.com%2Fswedish-artists-jail-term-extended-after-he-committed-hate-crime-of-saying-muslim-migrants-have-not-integrated%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23KWuvsqaYAq3n4n8dAIGDrgmlUwMbjWBVQPSoNbWvUOokuQxD-nxkZz4&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1SKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=cbb415e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infowars.com/swedish-artists-jail-term-extended-after-he-committed-hate-crime-of-saying-muslim-migrants-have-not-integrated/?fbclid=IwAR23KWuvsqaYAq3n4n8dAIGDrgmlUwMbjWBVQPSoNbWvUOokuQxD-nxkZz4</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇報導帶有偏右立場，但大家可以睇睇瑞典斯坦既問題。眾所周知，穆斯林移民大量遷入後，瑞典既強姦案係倍級增長，更成為北歐既強姦大國。"},{"pid":"030c3065a4d32c7ab18297bd7fff13141424d4c3","tid":1132523,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/man/Gossiping/D315/D2D3/D79C/D7A3/M.1442117541.A.C9C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fman%2FGossiping%2FD315%2FD2D3%2FD79C%2FD7A3%2FM.1442117541.A.C9C.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf